---
import Layout from 'src/layouts/Layout.astro';

export const prerender = true
---

<Layout 
  title="About SPLITDO | Blockchain Bill Splitting Platform on Solana"
  description="SPLITDO combines expense tracking with blockchain settlements. Split bills globally with Solana-powered instant payments and near-zero fees. Revolutionary crypto expense management platform."
  keywords="SPLITDO platform, blockchain bill splitting, crypto payments, Solana DeFi, expense management, about SPLITDO, crypto finance app"
  ogType="website"
>
  <style>
    .text-gradient {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #22d3ee 0%, #3b82f6 50%, #8b5cf6 100%);
      -webkit-background-clip: text;
      -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
      background-clip: text;
    }
  </style>

  <main class="bg-zinc-950 text-white min-h-screen">

    <!-- Hero -->
    <section class="py-24 sm:py-32 px-6 border-b border-zinc-800">
      <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto">
        <h1 class="text-5xl sm:text-6xl lg:text-7xl font-black mb-6">
          About<br/>
          <span class="text-gradient">SplitDo</span>
        </h1>
        <p class="text-xl text-zinc-400 max-w-2xl">
          We're on a mission to eliminate the hassle of splitting expenses through blockchain technology and smart automation.
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Stats -->
    <section class="border-b border-zinc-800">
      <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-6 py-12 sm:py-0">
        <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row sm:divide-x divide-zinc-800">
          <div class="py-4 sm:py-12 sm:flex-1 text-center">
            <div class="text-3xl sm:text-5xl font-black text-cyan-400">10M+</div>
            <div class="text-sm text-zinc-500 mt-1">Transactions</div>
          </div>
          <div class="py-4 sm:py-12 sm:flex-1 text-center">
            <div class="text-3xl sm:text-5xl font-black">50K+</div>
            <div class="text-sm text-zinc-500 mt-1">Users</div>
          </div>
          <div class="py-4 sm:py-12 sm:flex-1 text-center">
            <div class="text-3xl sm:text-5xl font-black">99.9%</div>
            <div class="text-sm text-zinc-500 mt-1">Uptime</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Story -->
    <section class="py-24 sm:py-32 px-6">
      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
        <h2 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-black mb-8">Our Story</h2>
        
        <div class="space-y-6 text-lg text-zinc-400 leading-relaxed">
          <p>
            SplitDo was born from a persistent frustration with expense tracking and splitting. For years, we witnessed the tedious process of coordinating payments when going out with friends or sending money to family.
          </p>
          <p>
            We wondered why no consolidated system had ever been created - not just for expense management, but for a comprehensive solution that could handle all aspects of shared financial interactions.
          </p>
          <p>
            Our team brought together expertise in blockchain technology, high-performance systems, and fintech operations. We saw the potential to create something extraordinary - a blockchain application built for real-world use.
          </p>
          <p>
            But we knew what the market needed: a product-centered company focused on user-first experiences. This led to creating a platform that combines cutting-edge blockchain technology with an intuitive interface that makes expense management as simple as taking a photo.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Mission -->
    <section class="py-24 sm:py-32 px-6 bg-zinc-900/50">
      <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto">
        <div class="mb-16">
          <h2 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-black mb-4">Our Mission</h2>
          <p class="text-xl text-zinc-500 max-w-2xl">
            To create a world where sharing expenses is effortless, transparent, and fair for everyone involved.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-12">
          <div>
            <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-cyan-500/10 flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
              <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-cyan-400" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M15 12a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0z"/>
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M2.458 12C3.732 7.943 7.523 5 12 5c4.478 0 8.268 2.943 9.542 7-1.274 4.057-5.064 7-9.542 7-4.477 0-8.268-2.943-9.542-7z"/>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3">Transparency</h3>
            <p class="text-zinc-500">
              Every transaction recorded on-chain. Complete visibility and accountability.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div>
            <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-cyan-500/10 flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
              <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-cyan-400" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M3 6l3 1m0 0l-3 9a5.002 5.002 0 006.001 0M6 7l3 9M6 7l6-2m6 2l3-1m-3 1l-3 9a5.002 5.002 0 006.001 0M18 7l3 9m-3-9l-6-2m0-2v2m0 16V5m0 16l-3-9m3 9l3-9"/>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3">Fairness</h3>
            <p class="text-zinc-500">
              Smart contracts ensure expenses are split exactly as agreed. No manipulation.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div>
            <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-cyan-500/10 flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
              <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-cyan-400" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z"/>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3">Simplicity</h3>
            <p class="text-zinc-500">
              Complex blockchain technology hidden behind an intuitive interface anyone can use.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Team -->
    <section class="py-24 sm:py-32 px-6">
      <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto">
        <div class="mb-16">
          <h2 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-black mb-4">Team</h2>
          <p class="text-xl text-zinc-500">
            Engineers, designers, and blockchain experts working to revolutionize expense management.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-1 gap-8 max-w-3xl">
          <!-- Anand -->
          <div class="flex items-start gap-6">
            <div class="w-20 h-20 bg-zinc-800 rounded-full overflow-hidden flex-shrink-0">
              <img src="/anand.png" alt="Anand Patel" class="w-full h-full object-cover" />
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="text-xl font-bold">Anand Patel</h3>
              <p class="text-cyan-400 text-sm font-medium mb-2">Chief Product Officer</p>
              <p class="text-zinc-500 text-sm">
                Product strategy lead with expertise in high-performance systems and user-first experiences.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- CTA -->
    <section class="py-24 sm:py-32 px-6 border-t border-zinc-800">
      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto text-center">
        <h2 class="text-4xl sm:text-5xl font-black mb-6">Join the Revolution</h2>
        <p class="text-xl text-zinc-400 mb-10">
          Experience the future of expense splitting. Download SplitDo today.
        </p>
        <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center">
          <a href="/download" class="px-10 py-4 bg-white text-zinc-950 font-bold">
            Download Now
          </a>
          <a href="/tokenomics" class="px-10 py-4 text-zinc-300 hover:text-white font-semibold border-b-2 border-transparent hover:border-cyan-500 transition-all">
            $SPLITDO Token
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

  </main>
</Layout>
